Name:           cosmic-wallpapers
Version:        1.0.0
%define beta alpha.7
Release:        %{?beta:0.%{beta}.}1
Group:          Wallpapers/COSMIC
Summary:        Wallpapers for the COSMIC Desktop Environment
License:        CC-BY-4.0 OR  CC0-1.0
URL:            https://github.com/pop-os/cosmic-wallpapers
